<h1>You Can Now Reapply for Your Visa Letter</h1>

<p>Hello <%= @participant.full_name %>,</p>

<p>Good news! Your visa letter application for <strong><%= @event.name %></strong> has been reviewed again, and you are now eligible to submit a new application.</p>

<% if @application.rejection_reason.present? %>
<h2>Previous Rejection Reason</h2>
<p><%= @application.rejection_reason %></p>
<p>Please address the above concerns in your new application.</p>
<% end %>

<h2>Reapply Now</h2>
<p>Click the button below to submit a new visa letter application:</p>
<p><a href="<%= @reapply_url %>" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #ec3750; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold;">Apply for Visa Letter</a></p>

<p>If you have any questions, please contact us at <%= @event.contact_email %>.</p>

<p>Best regards,<br>The Hack Club Team</p>
